    public final class IntToByteFixedMultiMap
extends PrimitiveMultiMap
implements PrimitiveScalarMultiMap
    A compact multi-map which allows one-time put of a fixed list of values. Adding more values is not supported.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
